; Coverage for history.cc line 233: alias_commodity early return (no graph_index)
; "E" is used before the commodity alias maps it to EUR
; The alias collision calls alias_commodity, but "E" has no price graph index

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Travel    500 E
    Assets:Checking

commodity EUR
    alias E

2024/01/02 Test2
    Expenses:Food    100 E
    Assets:Checking

test bal Expenses
               500 E
             100 EUR  Expenses
             100 EUR    Food
               500 E    Travel
--------------------
               500 E
             100 EUR
end test
